name: URLRequest
desc: A URL load request that is independent of protocol or URL scheme.

items.name: NSURLRequest.CachePolicy
items.desc: The constants used to specify interaction with the cached responses.

items.name: httpMethod
items.desc: The HTTP request method.

items.name: url
items.desc: The URL of the request.

items.name: httpBody
items.desc: The data sent as the message body of a request, such as for an HTTP POST request.

items.name: httpBodyStream
items.desc: The stream used to deliver the HTTP body.

items.name: mainDocumentURL
items.desc: The main document URL associated with this request.

items.name: allHTTPHeaderFields
items.desc: A dictionary containing all of the HTTP header fields for a request.

items.name: addValue
items.desc: Adds a value to the header field.

items.name: setValue
items.desc: Sets a value for the header field.

items.name: value
items.desc: Retrieves a header value.

items.name: timeoutInterval
items.desc: The timeout interval of the request.

items.name: httpShouldHandleCookies
items.desc: A Boolean value indicating whether cookies will be sent with and set for this request.

items.name: httpShouldUsePipelining
items.desc: A Boolean value indicating whether the request should transmit before the previous response is received.

items.name: allowsCellularAccess
items.desc: A Boolean value indicating whether the request is allowed to use the built-in cellular radios to satisfy the request.

items.name: allowsConstrainedNetworkAccess
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether the request may use the network when the user has specified Low Data Mode.

items.name: allowsExpensiveNetworkAccess
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether connections may use a network interface that the system considers expensive.

items.name: networkServiceType
items.desc: The service type associated with this request.

items.name: NSURLRequest.NetworkServiceType
items.desc: Constants that specify how a request uses network resources.

items.name: description
items.desc: A textual description of the request.

items.name: debugDescription
items.desc: A textual description of the request suitable for debugging.

items.name: customMirror
items.desc: A mirror that reflects the request.

items.name: hashValue
